These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, juice, lemonade, water
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, action, documentary, superhero
1. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
2. the person watching superhero movies is on the far left##1
3. the person watching documentary movies is between the person watching action movies and the person drinking juice##2
4. the person drinking water is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking cola##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | water         | juice   | lemonade | cola       |
| Movie-Genre      | superhero | zombie | documentary   | action |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
4 different games are played: whist, go, domino, snooker
There are 4 different nationalities: british, colombian, dutch, turkish
1. the turkish is between the person playing domino and the colombian##2
2. the person playing snooker is on the far right##1
3. the dutch is on the right of the british##1
4. the person playing whist is on the left of the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Game         | go | whist | domino | snooker |
| Nationality   | colombian    | turkish   | british | dutch       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
4 different games are played: canasta, domino, snooker, mah-jongg
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, british, colombian, french
1. the colombian is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
2. the colombian is between the british and the person playing domino##2
3. the british is on the far left##1
4. the french is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
5. the person playing domino is the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Game          | mah-jongg    | canasta | domino   | snooker  |
| Nationality   | british | colombian   | french | australian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-4::.
City: nizza, london, marseilles, hamburg
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, biathlon, rugby, tennis
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person traveling to london##1
2. the person traveling to nizza is between the person who's sport is basketball and the person traveling to hamburg##2
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far right##1
4. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3      |    4     |
| City     | hamburg   | nizza    | marseilles       | london   |
| Sport   | rugby | tennis | basketball | biathlon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, soy-milk
4 different pets are kept: snake, hamster, ferret, guinea-pig
1. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the owner of the ferret is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the snake is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is between the owner of the snake and the owner of the hamster##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2     |     3     |       4       |
| Beverage   | fanta        | iced-tea | soy-milk  | hot-chocolate |
| Pet      | ferret | hamster  | guinea-pig | snake    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, d&b, pop, salsa
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, satire, superhero, martial-arts
1. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
2. the fan of salsa is the person watching superhero movies##1
3. the fan of salsa is on the far right##1
4. the fan of d&b is the person watching romance movies##1
5. the fan of pop is between the fan of classical and the fan of d&b##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | d&b     | pop           | classical | salsa  |
| Movie-Genre         | romance | martial-arts | satire   | superhero |

