.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, gospel, house, punk
4 different games are played: scrabble, bridge, snooker, poker
1. the fan of gospel is the person playing scrabble##1
2. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
3. the person playing poker is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
4. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing poker##1
5. the fan of electronic is between the person playing scrabble and the fan of house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | punk   | gospel | electronic | house      |
| Game     | snooker | scrabble    | bridge  | poker |

