.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, lavender, chestnut, fuchsia
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, roller, snowmobile
1. the person driving the helicopter is the person who likes lavender##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is between the person who likes chestnut and the person driving the roller##2
3. the person who likes aquamarine is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Color       | aquamarine | fuchsia | chestnut     | lavender   |
| Transport   | roller   | motorbike     | snowmobile | helicopter |

