.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, entrepreneur, librarian, videographer
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, lettuce, pepper, grapes
1. the librarian is between the person eating eggplant and the dressmaker##2
2. the person eating grapes is on the left of the dressmaker##1
3. the videographer is on the right of the dressmaker##1
4. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
5. the dressmaker is on the left of the person eating pepper##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | entrepreneur | librarian | dressmaker | videographer |
| Food   | eggplant         | grapes       | lettuce    | pepper         |

