.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, action, adventure, epic
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, ice-hockey, swimming, tennis
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
3. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is between the person watching action movies and the person who's sport is tennis##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Movie-Genre    | epic   | adventure      | action   | crime  |
| Sport   | tennis | ice-hockey | swimming | baseball |

