.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, cauliflower, lime, onion
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, ebony, chestnut, brown
1. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
2. the person eating cauliflower is between the person eating onion and the person eating apple##2
3. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
4. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person eating apple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Food          | apple     | cauliflower | onion   | lime        |
| Color   | grey | chestnut   | ebony | brown |

