2. the owner of the rat is between the owner of the frog and the owner of the rabbit##2
3. the librarian is on the right of the doctor##1
4. the owner of the frog is on the right of the librarian##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |
| Job           | doctor | librarian | firefighter | entrepreneur |
| Pet   | rabbit   | rat | frog         | hedgehog |

