2. the farmhouse house is the person driving the scooter##1
3. the palace house is between the person driving the scooter and the ranch-style house##2
4. the farmhouse house is on the right of the palace house##1
5. the person driving the bike is on the left of the ranch-style house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |   3    |    4     |
| House   | wooden | ranch-style | palace | farmhouse |
| Transport     | bike     | bus   | subway | scooter  |

