.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
House: palace, colonial, cape-cod, wooden
4 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, goat, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1
2. the palace house is between the owner of the cat and the wooden house##2
3. the wooden house is on the left of the palace house##1
4. the colonial house is on the far right##1
5. the colonial house is on the right of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| House   | cape-cod    | wooden     | palace | colonial |
| Pet     | chinchilla | guinea-pig | goat       | cat     |

 